<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="21Jun1928"><font color="red">21 June 1928</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Have just finished (11.55 a.m) final &amp; fifth revision of <font face="wake">D</font>b. What a job! I shall write as soon as I get breath. Can you please copy the missing words and phrases on to one copy of t12 tear them out and send them to me as I want to put them in my book? &hellip; I hope you will like the compli wangler <font face="wake">D</font>b when you see him &hellip; epistolically yours </div>
